        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Eef2k is enriched in the PSD fraction.\n- \" eEF2/CaMKIII was highly concentrated in the PSD fraction, while PDK was not detected in the PSD fraction but in the dendritic lipid raft and SPM fraction. \". Experimental description: \"Synaptic plasma membrane (SPM), postsynaptic density (PSD) and dendritic lipid raft fractions were prepared from the forebrains of Wistar rats (6 weeks old, male)...\" p. 169" ;
